(3886, 450, 'detail', 'What are Plastic gusset food bags on roll?\r\nPlastic gusset food bags on roll are bags that can be expanded on both sides. The purpose is to increase the storage area of the bag. This type of bag can be a die cut, flat or T shirt.\r\n\r\nThe bags are rolled in 1 roll and separated by a cut line. When used, the user will jerk off at that cut line.\r\n\r\nSpecifications of Plastic gusset food bags on roll\r\n1. Thickness\r\nBecause these are food bags, food safety and hygiene are put on top. Materials to produce Plastic gusset food bags on roll are usually HDPE, LDPE, MDPE.\r\n\r\nTypically, the bags are manufactured from HDPE material with a thickness ranging from 6 to 40mic. High quality LDPE material can be used to make thickness from 15 to 200mic. The MDPE type can produce 8 to 40 mic bags.\r\n\r\nThe thickness of Plastic gusset food bags on roll can be customized according to customer needs.\r\n\r\n2. Degradation\r\nThe self degradation ability of Plastic gusset food bags on roll is a very important factor to protect the environment of the country as well as the whole world. Therefore, it is a favorite in many countries and even required.\r\n\r\nVn Plastic can produce degradable bags with EPI, D2W… features. The percentage of degradation particles can be customized depending on the needs of the importer.\r\n\r\n3. Width\r\nThe width of Plastic gusset food bags on roll depends on whether the production material is LDPE, HDPE or MDPE. If the bag is manufactured from LDPE, the width will range from 160 to 650mm. Particularly for HDPE or MDPE materials, the width will be 160 to 450mm.'),
