(504, 1, '2021-09-09 03:10:07', '2021-09-09 03:10:07', '<header class=\"entry-header\">\r\n<div class=\"entry-image relative\"><a href=\"https://vnplast.com/pe-plastic-bags-in-vietnam/\"><img class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-post-image lazy-load-active\" src=\"https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Most-popular-PE-plastic-bags-in-Vietnam.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 840px) 100vw, 840px\" srcset=\"https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Most-popular-PE-plastic-bags-in-Vietnam.jpg 840w, https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Most-popular-PE-plastic-bags-in-Vietnam-768x512.jpg 768w, https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Most-popular-PE-plastic-bags-in-Vietnam-800x533.jpg 800w\" alt=\"Most popular PE plastic bags in Vietnam\" width=\"840\" height=\"560\" data-src=\"https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Most-popular-PE-plastic-bags-in-Vietnam.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Most-popular-PE-plastic-bags-in-Vietnam.jpg 840w, https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Most-popular-PE-plastic-bags-in-Vietnam-768x512.jpg 768w, https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Most-popular-PE-plastic-bags-in-Vietnam-800x533.jpg 800w\" /></a></div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class=\"entry-content single-page\">\r\n<div id=\"ftwp-container-outer\" class=\"ftwp-in-post ftwp-float-right\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"ftwp-postcontent\">\r\n\r\nPE plastic bags in Vietnam have many types such as t shirt, flat, bag on roll, block header or sheet. Each type has its own use purpose. In addition, whether plastic bags are biodegradable is also a very important factor today, especially in developed countries such as US or Europe.\r\n<h2 id=\"ftoc-heading-1\" class=\"ftwp-heading\">PE plastic T shirt bags</h2>\r\nT shirt bag also known as vest carrier bag. This is a PE bag with 2 handles on both sides. One can also be designed additional hanging holes on each side. This type of bag is arranged in blocks. Each block can be 25 pieces, 50 or up to 100 pieces. Each bag can also have additional features such as emboss or side gusset.\r\n\r\n<em>Read more: <a href=\"https://vnplast.com/plastic-t-shirt-food-bags-on-roll/\">Plastic T shirt Bag</a></em>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_925\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-925\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-925 lazy-load-active\" src=\"https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/T-shirt-food-bags-on-roll.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/T-shirt-food-bags-on-roll.jpg 800w, https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/T-shirt-food-bags-on-roll-768x768.jpg 768w, https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/T-shirt-food-bags-on-roll-400x400.jpg 400w, https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/T-shirt-food-bags-on-roll-100x100.jpg 100w\" alt=\"Plastic T shirt food bags on roll\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" data-src=\"https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/T-shirt-food-bags-on-roll.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/T-shirt-food-bags-on-roll.jpg 800w, https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/T-shirt-food-bags-on-roll-768x768.jpg 768w, https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/T-shirt-food-bags-on-roll-400x400.jpg 400w, https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/T-shirt-food-bags-on-roll-100x100.jpg 100w\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-925\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Plastic T shirt food bags on roll</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '5 túi nhựa PE phổ biến nhất tại Việt Nam', 'PE plastic bags in Vietnam have many types such as t shirt, flat, bag on roll, block header or sheet. Each type has its own use purpose. In addition', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '146-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-09-09 03:10:07', '2021-09-09 03:10:07', '', 146, 'http://vnplast.wecan-group.info/?p=504', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(505, 1, '2021-09-09 03:10:30', '2021-09-09 03:10:30', '<header class=\"entry-header\">\r\n<div class=\"entry-image relative\"><a href=\"https://vnplast.com/post-consumer-vs-post-industrial-plastic-waste/\"><img class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-post-image lazy-load-active\" src=\"https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Post-consumer-vs-post-industrial-plastic-waste-in-Vietnam-2.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 840px) 100vw, 840px\" srcset=\"https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Post-consumer-vs-post-industrial-plastic-waste-in-Vietnam-2.jpg 840w, https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Post-consumer-vs-post-industrial-plastic-waste-in-Vietnam-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Post-consumer-vs-post-industrial-plastic-waste-in-Vietnam-2-800x533.jpg 800w\" alt=\"Post consumer vs post industrial plastic waste in Vietnam\" width=\"840\" height=\"560\" data-src=\"https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Post-consumer-vs-post-industrial-plastic-waste-in-Vietnam-2.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Post-consumer-vs-post-industrial-plastic-waste-in-Vietnam-2.jpg 840w, https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Post-consumer-vs-post-industrial-plastic-waste-in-Vietnam-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Post-consumer-vs-post-industrial-plastic-waste-in-Vietnam-2-800x533.jpg 800w\" /></a></div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class=\"entry-content single-page\">\r\n<div id=\"ftwp-container-outer\" class=\"ftwp-in-post ftwp-float-right\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"ftwp-postcontent\">\r\n\r\nPost consumer VS post industrial plastic waste have a big differences both in value and their origin. Plastic recycling is now a global trend. It is playing a big role in reducing plastic waste into the environment in Vietnam as well as around the world. So, what are the differences between them? Let’s learn more about this in this article with <a href=\"https://vnplast.com/\">Vn Plastic</a>.\r\n<h2 id=\"ftoc-heading-1\" class=\"ftwp-heading\">Post consumer plastic waste in Vietnam</h2>\r\nPost consumer plastic waste in Vietnam is finished plastic bag, already used by consumer. That waste is then collected and recycled using industrial methods.\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_1249\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1249\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-1249 lazy-load-active\" src=\"https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Post-consumer-plastic-waste-in-Vietnam-2.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 840px) 100vw, 840px\" srcset=\"https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Post-consumer-plastic-waste-in-Vietnam-2.jpg 840w, https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Post-consumer-plastic-waste-in-Vietnam-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Post-consumer-plastic-waste-in-Vietnam-2-800x533.jpg 800w\" alt=\"Post consumer plastic waste in Vietnam\" width=\"840\" height=\"560\" data-src=\"https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Post-consumer-plastic-waste-in-Vietnam-2.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Post-consumer-plastic-waste-in-Vietnam-2.jpg 840w, https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Post-consumer-plastic-waste-in-Vietnam-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://vnplast.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Post-consumer-plastic-waste-in-Vietnam-2-800x533.jpg 800w\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1249\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Post consumer plastic waste in Vietnam</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Hậu tiêu dùng vs rác thải nhựa công nghiệp tại Việt Nam', 'Post consumer plastic waste in Vietnam is finished plastic bag, already used by consumer. That waste is then collected and recycled using industrial methods.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '143-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-09-09 03:10:30', '2021-09-09 03:10:30', '', 143, 'http://vnplast.wecan-group.info/?p=505', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
